{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我们有点小小的问题
We have a little problem.

493
00:31:30,218 --> 00:31:32,510
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}关上窗户这里会特别热
It's extremely hot in here with the windows closed

494
00:31:32,583 --> 00:31:35,409
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}开着又会特别吵
and extremely noisy with them open.

495
00:31:35,481 --> 00:31:38,042
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}所以，我想能不能请你们
So, I was wondering if there was any way you could,

496
00:31:38,042 --> 00:31:41,601
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}先修别的地方，大概45分钟就好?
I don't know, maybe work someplace else for about 45 minutes?

497
