1121
01:23:15,272 --> 01:23:17,832
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}变成疯子也让我找到一点儿乐子
There's no point in being nuts if you can't have a little fun.

1122
01:23:18,000 --> 01:23:19,000
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}天啊，约翰
Jesus Christ, John.

1123
01:23:19,700 --> 01:23:21,000
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}真被你唬到了
You know, I should have known.

1124
01:23:23,672 --> 01:23:24,532
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}药在这里
Here you go.

1125
01:23:27,102 --> 01:23:28,201
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我想等下再吃
I can take those later.

1126
01:23:28,201 --> 01:23:29,786
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你现在就该吃了
You're supposed to take them now.

1127
01:23:31,032 --> 01:23:33,088
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我给你拿点什么喝?
Can I bring you something?

1128
01:23:33,131 --> 01:23:34,418
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}不用麻烦了
I'm okay.

1129
01:23:35,080 --> 01:23:36,180
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}好
Okay.

1130
01:23:39,494 --> 01:23:41,780
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}唔，我...我是来这里
So, yeah. I... I was in town

1131
01:23:41,780 --> 01:23:43,980
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}主持一个研讨会
giving a workshop.

1132
01:23:43,980 --> 01:23:45,781
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}今晚就得回去
I go back tonight.

1133
01:23:45,854 --> 01:23:48,947
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你知道的，本德尔，他很想来
You know, Bender, he really wanted

1134
01:23:48,947 --> 01:23:53,210
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}拜访一下，看看你，打个照面
to stop by and you know, see you. You know, say hi.

1135
01:23:53,210 --> 01:23:55,180
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}但他害怕?
Squeamish?

1136
01:23:56,180 --> 01:23:57,180
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}是的
Yeah.

1137
01:23:57,180 --> 01:23:59,338
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}估计换作是我也一样
I suppose I would be, too.

1138
01:23:59,410 --> 01:24:02,428
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}可是哎呀，我却被自己缠上了
But alas, I'm stuck with me.

1139
01:24:05,007 --> 01:24:08,366
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我正试着解决黎曼假设
I'm trying to solve the Riemann Hypothesis.

1140
01:24:10,137 --> 01:24:11,291
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}喔，是吗?
Oh, yeah?

1141
01:24:11,534 --> 01:24:15,393
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我觉得要是...要是我能让他们刮目相看
I figured if... if I dazzle them,

1142
01:24:15,393 --> 01:24:17,451
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}他们就该让我复职了
they will have to reinstate me.

1143
01:24:19,296 --> 01:24:22,703
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}但因为药物的影响就很困难
But it's difficult with the medication,

1144
01:24:22,703 --> 01:24:26,112
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}很难看出...
because it's hard to...

1145
01:24:28,355 --> 01:24:29,783
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}它的解
see the solution.

1146
01:24:38,481 --> 01:24:40,942
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}知道吗，约翰，你应该放松的
You know, John, you should go easy.

1147
01:24:41,578 --> 01:24:44,380
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}还有许多别的事可做...
There are other things besides...

1148
01:24:44,380 --> 01:24:45,680
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}除了工作
Besides work.

1149
01:24:48,373 --> 01:24:49,801
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}都有什么呢?
What are they?

1150
01:25:25,879 --> 01:25:27,535
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你在想什么呢?
What are you thinking about?

1151
01:25:31,940 --> 01:25:33,227
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}人们都做些什么?
What do people do?

1152
01:25:33,605 --> 01:25:35,289
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}都在生活，约翰
It's life, John.

1153
01:25:36,171 --> 01:25:37,765
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}做可以做的事情
Activities available,

1154
01:25:37,835 --> 01:25:40,127
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}增添一点儿意义
just add meaning.

1155
01:25:48,161 --> 01:25:50,089
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你可以试着走出家门
You could try leaving the house.

1156
01:25:51,291 --> 01:25:53,880
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}或许可以...
You know, maybe...

1157
01:25:53,880 --> 01:25:55,980
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}和邻居们闲聊
talk to people.

1158
01:26:00,251 --> 01:26:02,236
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你可以试着把垃圾拿出去
You could try taking out the garbage.

1159
01:26:24,836 --> 01:26:29,036
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}那儿还有一些...还有一些在...
And there's some more... there's some more in...

1160
01:26:40,254 --> 01:26:43,177
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你...你在跟谁讲话?
Who... Who were you talking to?

1161
01:26:43,551 --> 01:26:44,679
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}收垃圾的人
Garbage man.

1162
01:26:54,077 --> 01:26:56,069
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}收垃圾的人晚上不来的
Garbage men don't come at night.

1163
01:26:59,206 --> 01:27:00,963
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}也许这一块儿的回来
I guess around here they do.

1164
01:27:27,718 --> 01:27:29,642
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}对不起
Sorry.

1165
01:28:35,599 --> 01:28:37,224
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}是因为吃药的关系吗?
Is it the medication?

1166
01:29:18,398 --> 01:29:20,757
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我不知道该怎么办
I don't know what to do.

1167
01:29:38,650 --> 01:29:41,578
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}今晚上我妈带孩子会带久一点
My mother's going to keep the baby a little longer tonight.

1168
01:29:42,881 --> 01:29:45,036
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}这样我就能再加三小时的班
I can get three hours of overtime.

1169
01:30:11,592 --> 01:30:13,248
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我去睡了
I'm going to bed.

1170
01:30:20,218 --> 01:30:22,476
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}-晚安  -晚安
-Good night.  -Good night.

1171
01:31:41,522 --> 01:31:44,075
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}很高兴见到你，约翰
It's good to see you, John.

1172
01:31:44,953 --> 01:31:46,540
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}好久不见了
It's been a while.

1173
01:31:47,518 --> 01:31:48,572
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}帕彻?
Parcher?

1174
01:31:49,149 --> 01:31:50,577
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}是的，长官
Yes, sir.

1175
01:31:54,579 --> 01:31:55,735
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你不是真的!
You're not real!

1176
01:31:55,878 --> 01:31:58,533
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我当然是，别说胡话了
Of course I am. Don't be ridiculous.

1177
01:32:03,106 --> 01:32:05,567
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我觉得我是不会走那边的，约翰
I don't think that I would go that way, John.

1178
01:32:07,103 --> 01:32:09,429
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}是时候让你回来工作了
It's time for you to get back to work.

1179
01:32:09,934 --> 01:32:11,780
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}原子弹已经抵达最终位置了
The bomb is in its final position

1180
01:32:11,780 --> 01:32:13,780
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}就在美国境内
here in the U.S.

1181
01:32:15,596 --> 01:32:16,789
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我们知道你的状况
Knowing your situation

1182
01:32:16,789 --> 01:32:19,980
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你不得不保持低调，先知
requires you keep a low profile, "Mohammed",

1183
01:32:21,125 --> 01:32:23,717
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}所以我们为了你搬过来了
we've brought the mountain to you.

1184
01:32:42,609 --> 01:32:44,559
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我们把原子弹的位置范围
We've narrowed the bomb's location

1185
01:32:44,559 --> 01:32:46,371
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}缩小到东部沿海某地了
to somewhere on the eastern seaboard.

1186
01:32:48,371 --> 01:32:51,423
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}可是一直没法找出确定的地点
But we haven't been able to pinpoint its exact position.

1187
01:32:53,833 --> 01:32:56,522
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}他们的密码越来越复杂了
Their codes have grown increasingly complex.

1188
01:32:59,629 --> 01:33:01,319
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}来，看看这个，约翰
Here, look at this, John.

1189
01:33:04,160 --> 01:33:05,152
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}怎么?
What?

1190
01:33:06,190 --> 01:33:07,316
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}怎么?
What?

1191
01:33:10,021 --> 01:33:11,147
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}罗森医生说...
Dr. Rosen said...

1192
01:33:11,147 --> 01:33:12,616
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}罗森! 那个江湖郎中!
Rosen! That quack!

1193
01:33:13,518 --> 01:33:15,380
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}"精神分裂症导致虚构现实"，对不对?
"Schizophrenic break from reality," right?

1194
01:33:15,380 --> 01:33:19,100
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}心理医生的屁话! 看着我，约翰
Psychological bullshit! Look at me, John.

1195
01:33:20,880 --> 01:33:22,380
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}约翰，看着我
John, look at me.

1196
01:33:24,376 --> 01:33:25,929
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我看着像幻觉吗?
Do I look like I'm imagined?

1197
01:33:28,677 --> 01:33:30,367
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}惠勒研究室没有你的资料
Wheeler has no record of you.

1198
01:33:30,476 --> 01:33:32,461
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你觉得我们会留人事资料?
Do you think we list our personnel?

1199
01:33:35,273 --> 01:33:37,666
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}约翰，对不起让你经历这一切
John, I'm sorry you had to go through all this.

1200
01:33:39,135 --> 01:33:41,688
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我花了很大一番功夫才把你弄回来
I've gone to a great deal of trouble to get you back.

1201
01:33:42,166 --> 01:33:44,889
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我可以恢复你在惠勒研究室的身份
I can restore your status at Wheeler.

1202
01:33:44,964 --> 01:33:47,687
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我可以让世界知道你的贡献
I can let the world know what you did.

1203
01:33:47,762 --> 01:33:49,849
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}但我现在需要你，士兵
But I need you now, soldier.

1204
01:33:56,322 --> 01:33:58,250
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}当时以为你不是真的可把我吓坏了
I was so scared you weren't real.

1205
