{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}暴风雨要来了
There's a storm coming.

1207
01:34:08,450 --> 01:34:11,150
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我去把衣服收进来，好吗?
I'm just going to grab the laundry, okay?

