Charles, you've been a very good friend to me.

1407
01:51:55,359 --> 01:51:57,116
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}最好的
The best.

1408
01:51:58,490 --> 01:52:00,418
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}但我不会再跟你说话了
