02:03:05,311 --> 02:03:07,164
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}在主席台上跳舞
Dance around the podium,

1566
02:03:07,164 --> 02:03:09,835
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}一丝不挂然后学鸡叫，类似这种?
strip naked and squawk like a chicken, things of this nature?

1567
02:03:10,107 --> 02:03:12,228
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}差不多啦，嗯
