1585
02:04:28,880 --> 02:04:30,036
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}教授
Professor.

1586
02:04:35,409 --> 02:04:37,337
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}干得好，约翰
Nicely done, John.

1587
02:04:37,407 --> 02:04:38,664
