1593
02:05:26,635 --> 02:05:28,359
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}谢谢大家
Thank you.

1594
02:05:32,397 --> 02:05:34,350
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我一直相信数字
I've always believed in numbers.

1595
02:05:35,650 --> 02:05:37,250
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}在方程和逻辑学中
In the equations and logics

1596
02:05:37,250 --> 02:05:39,250
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}它都指向一切的缘由
that lead to reason.

1597
02:05:40,358 --> 02:05:42,513
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}但经过终生的求索
But after a lifetime of such pursuits,

1598
02:05:43,656 --> 02:05:47,142
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我问自己，逻辑到底是什么?
I ask, what truly is logic?

1599
02:05:48,819 --> 02:05:50,247
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}谁决定了缘由?
Who decides reason?

1600
02:05:52,350 --> 02:05:55,550
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}我的追求带着我遍历了实体世界
My quest has taken me through the physical,

1601
02:05:55,550 --> 02:05:57,450
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}形而上学
the metaphysical,

1602
02:05:59,210 --> 02:06:00,638
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}幻觉
the delusional,

1603
02:06:02,874 --> 02:06:04,359
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}又回到原点
and back.

1604
02:06:05,973 --> 02:06:08,901
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}而我有了生涯中最重要的发现
And I have made the most important discovery of my career.

1605
02:06:11,567 --> 02:06:13,825
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}生命中最重要的发现
The most important discovery of my life.

1606
02:06:17,296 --> 02:06:20,451
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}那就是只有在爱的神秘方程中
