1610
02:06:38,747 --> 02:06:40,675
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}你是我所有一切的缘由
You are all my reasons.

1611
02:06:45,242 --> 02:06:46,499
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}谢谢你
Thank you.

1612
02:07:41,033 --> 02:07:42,961
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}非常幸会
So nice to have met you.

1613
