02:07:53,623 --> 02:07:56,244
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}早就准备好了
Yes, indeed, and yes, please.

1618
02:07:56,321 --> 02:07:58,249
{\3c&H000000&\bord1.5\fn微软雅黑}真谢谢你
Thank you so much.

1619
